    "object_type": "text",
    "current_location": "Convergence",
    "excerpt": "No matter what city or town or part of the country Betita lived in, she made special contributions and created life-long memories. One of her greatest assets was her ability to inspire and mentor young people. Here in New Mexico she passed on her knowledge and skills to scores of <em>jovenes</em> in the Movimiento Chicano.",
    "collection": "martinez",
